{"tid":1386782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夢遊想食好西嘅小朋友請你入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T01:28:19.000Z","uid":280901,"like":227,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"93da2aa52639fceffffbb30a3fd422dababd860a","tid":1386782,"uid":280901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"[代朋友po]<br />\n<br />\n各位夢遊小孩，叔叔我年紀大，無大家咁好力氣，未必下下衝到去前線，但我實在唔忍心見到你地咁辛苦餓住個肚上前線，所以我希望用自己手廚藝黎慰勞下、支持下你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道有其它叔叔姨姨都準備緊禮券食物券，但都想畀多個選擇你地揀。我地呢排廚房佬既一技之長就係提供<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MURm8sQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMURm8sQ.png&h=aa436e26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuH18sQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuH18sQ.png&h=d85d4df7&s={SIZE}\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我打算係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今個星期日，港島地區供應大約300份</span></span>。到時會有幾個一齊夢遊既後生仔幫我手送到前線既手上，行到攰既，可以隨時黎拎嘢食，食飽食好再上陣！如果你地覺得好食嘅，我就更感恩啦！<br />\n<br />\n另外，每樣食物嘅包裝會印上識別碼，以作辨認。詳情會係星期五再開po公布。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n你地真係唔好怕醜，我地班廢中要你地小朋友出黎頂，我地實在好慚愧，所以你地唔使客氣隨便拎嘢食，要食好休息好呀！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935a6478fb8bf4a6e58de17aaf186b42a550f5e2","tid":1386782,"uid":254923,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"睇到都好撚正 多謝您地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad7ba8129c23b94f8a98ed1adc041346f9272cb","tid":1386782,"uid":280901,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"93da2aa52639fceffffbb30a3fd422dababd860a","tid":1386782,"uid":280901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"[代朋友po]<br />\n<